title: DR. MARTENS X TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES: MICHELANGELO
description:
Dr. Martens have teamed up with Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles to create a 4-piece capsule collection inspired by the four characters.

The Mikey boot, inspired by Michelangelo. He stands for double pepperoni.
